"readTime":1,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_639f093f","title":"发布：datasette-ports 0.1","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Apr/6/datasette-ports/#atom-everything","date":"2026-04-06 00:23:55","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_639f093f.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":1,"score":78},{"id":"RAW_95914716","title":"GitHub Copilot CLI 结合不同模型系列提供“第二意见”","link":"https://github.blog/ai-and-ml/github-copilot/github-copilot-cli-combines-model-families-for-a-second-opinion/","date":"2026-04-06 21:53:51","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_95914716.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The GitHub Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":4,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_dc8e4f80","title":"如何将 JavaScript 中的 API 调用从“玩具级”提升至生产就绪的网络通信","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-go-from-toy-api-calls-to-production-ready-networking-in-javascript/","date":"2026-04-06 21:45:49","oneSentenceSummary":"一份关于如何将 JavaScript 网络通信从基础的 fetch() 调用演进为生产就绪模式的综合指南，涵盖了请求取消、错误处理、重试机制以及高级弹性策略。","summary":"本文旨在填补 JavaScript 中简单 API 调用与稳健生产级网络通信之间的鸿沟。文章从 fetch() 的基础知识入手，逐步引入了关键模式：使用 AbortController 防止响应乱序，处理除网络故障之外的 HTTP 错误，以及利用 ky 等库实现带有指数退避（exponential backoff）的自动重试机制。此外，文章还探讨了诸如速率限制、断路器（circuit breakers）和通过 ffetch 进行请求合并（request coalescing）等高级弹性模式，最后总结了从 HTTP 标头到基于存储的实现等各种缓存策略，以优化性能和可靠性。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_dc8e4f80.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_ef0d0680","title":"如何使用 OpenClaw 构建并保护个人 AI 智能体","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-build-and-secure-a-personal-ai-agent-with-openclaw/","date":"2026-04-06 21:44:44","oneSentenceSummary":"一份全面的技术指南，介绍了如何使用开源框架 OpenClaw 构建、配置和保护个人 AI 智能体，涵盖了其三层架构以及实用的生活管理自动化应用。","summary":"本文深入介绍了 OpenClaw，这是一个开源的个人 AI 智能体系统，旨在处理账单追踪和日程管理等现实任务。文章解释了由通道（Channel）、大脑（Brain）和身体（Body）层组成的核心架构，并详细阐述了七阶段智能体循环——从通道标准化和上下文组装，到 ReAct（推理 + 行动）循环。指南涵盖了安装过程、通过 Markdown 文件（SOUL.md、USER.md、AGENTS.md）定义智能体身份，以及连接 WhatsApp 等通信渠道。关键在于，文章强调了安全性，提供了防御提示词注入、未经授权的访问和凭据窃取的具体配置，同时讨论了涉及云端 LLM 和通过 Ollama 运行的本地实例的模型策略。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_ef0d0680.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_a648dda5","title":"如何在 Kubernetes 中对用户进行身份验证：x509 证书、OIDC 和云身份","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-authenticate-users-in-kubernetes-x509-certificates-oidc-and-cloud-identity/","date":"2026-04-06 20:31:43","oneSentenceSummary":"一份关于 Kubernetes 身份验证机制的深度技术指南，涵盖了内部身份验证器链、x509 证书实现以及与 Dex 的现代 OIDC 集成。","summary":"本文从第一性原理出发，解释了 Kubernetes 在没有内部用户数据库的情况下如何处理身份。文章探讨了可插拔的身份验证器链，区分了面向机器的 Service Account 和外部管理的 User。作者提供了创建 x509 客户端证书的实操演示，强调了其局限性（如缺乏吊销机制），并详细介绍了如何使用 Dex 和 kubelogin 设置用于生产环境的、基于浏览器的 OIDC (OpenID Connect) 登录。文中特别提到了 Kubernetes v1.30 中引入的现代 AuthenticationConfiguration，使其成为当前基础设施安全实践中极具参考价值的资源。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_a648dda5.json","topicTag":"devops","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":22,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_124f4108","title":"Vercel AI Gateway 零数据留存功能","link":"https://vercel.com/blog/zdr-on-ai-gateway","date":"2026-04-06 20:02:03","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_124f4108.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Vercel News","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_8404488c","title":"在 AI 时代，我是如何深入学习一个技术领域的","link":"https://tw93.fun/2026-04-06/learn.html","date":"2026-04-06 17:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/04/RAW_8404488c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Tw93 Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":7,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_ad7093a5","title":"每个 MLOps 工程师都应该了解的模型打包工具","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.